name: TEN20 Pixie Dress
description:
Made of stretchy cotton and lycra, dress is hot pink color. Bottom half of the dress is fringed with colorful pony beads, upper half of dress on the left breast, is decorated, with metal punk-like studs, right side has "TEN20" logo painted with silver fabric paint.

Spagettii straps, and string tie in the back of dress.
This dress is soft, comfy, short, and super cute!
size Small, fits about a size 2/4
One left
